      <title>Robinhood 的加密货币交易量下降速度快于竞争对手交易所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/robinhood-s-crypto-trading-volume-falls-faster-than-rival-exchanges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着散户投资者对数字资产的兴趣降温，Robinhood Markets Inc. 的加密货币交易量 4 月份减少了一半以上，超过了竞争对手交易所的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/robinhood-s-crypto-trading-volume-falls-faster-than-rival-exchanges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 15:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
